  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You point your finger towards a creature within range that you can see and whisper a message. The target (and only the target) hears the message and can reply in a whisper that only you can hear. You can cast this genjutsu through solid objects if you are familiar with the target and know it is beyond the barrier. This jutsu doesn't have to follow a straight line and can travel freely around corners or through openings.</p>",
